In summary, the realisation involved the following steps:

 1. investigating the Lake Federation property and the relevant planning scheme and restrictions;
 2. seeking advice on various issues affecting some of the relevant parcels of land;
 3. obtaining of an independent valuation of the Lake Federation property;
 4. seeking expert advice from sales agents as to the best means to sell the property; and 
 5. undertaking the sale of the property by a tender process and subsequent negotiation.
